2. _Even-Odd Check_

num = 7
if num % 2 == 0:
    print("Number is even")
else:
    print("Number is odd")


3. _Grade Checker_

marks = 85
if marks >= 90:
    print("Grade: A")
elif marks >= 80:
    print("Grade: B")
else:
    print("Grade: C")


